**&quot;Persicus Maximus&quot; (&quot;great victor over the Persians&quot;), 298
**&quot;Britannicus Maximus&quot; (&quot;great victor in Britain&quot;), 297
**&quot;Carpicus Maximus&quot; (&quot;great victor over Carpians&quot;), 297
